          "text": "I use Apple Logic Pro for all my recordings. It has a great collection of vintage softsynths. When I used Windows, I favored Sony ACID Pro 7.0 for music composition. It was the best loop-based software I found. While most DAWs today support loops, ACIDâ€™s streamlined interface never got in the way of creativity."
